# Generative AI PowerPoint Generator

Generative AI PowerPoint Generator is a web application that leverages Generative AI techniques to automatically generate PowerPoint presentations based on user-provided topics. This project utilizes llama2 and langchain libraries for content generation. The application is built using Python 3 and is hosted on Streamlit.

## Table of Contents

